PRIVACY POLICY
Bytes Survey App
At Bytes Survey, we are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and disclose information when you use our mobile application ("App").
1.	Information We Collect:
a.	Personal Information: We collect your phone number and full name for account management, communication, payment facilitation, personalization, fraud prevention, and data management purposes.
b.	Device Information: We collect device IDs for advertisement purposes.
2.	Use of Information:
a.	We use collected information to provide and improve our services, including facilitating surveys, processing payments, and personalizing user experiences.
b.	We do not share collected data with third parties.
3.	Survey Participation:
a.	Users are encouraged to participate in surveys voluntarily. Responses to survey questions are used solely for research purposes and do not identify individual users.
4.	Advertisement:
a.	Our App may contain advertisements from external sources. These advertisements are for informational purposes only and do not influence survey responses or user rewards.
5.	Payment:
a.	Users will be paid for their participation in surveys through their preferred payment method. Payment communication will be conducted using the phone number provided during account registration.
6.	Security:
a.	We implement appropriate security measures to protect against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction of collected data.
7.	Children's Privacy:
a.	Our services are not intended for children under the age of 17. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 17. If you believe we have collected personal information from a child under 17, please contact us immediately.
8.	Changes to Privacy Policy:
a.	We reserve the right to update or change our Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be effective immediately upon posting the revised Privacy Policy on our App.
Contact Us:
If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy, please contact us at axisgraphics1@gmail.com
NB: By using our App, you consent to the collection and use of information as outlined in this Privacy Policy.
